Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里迪安的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Photograph, Karidian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,两张照片对比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now photograph, both.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识雷顿博士，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know Dr. Leighton, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看待他的判断？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you say he's given to fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一位经验丰富的科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A good empirical research scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,稳重，名声好，有时会有伟大的发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steady, reputable, occasionally brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆力也特别好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With a very long memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我不太清楚，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have no information on that, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经准备好驶离轨道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are ready to leave orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不忙着离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll delay departure for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我要重回那个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm beaming back down to the planet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 汤姆在哪？ - 他去城里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where's Tom? - He went to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他来电说他正在回来的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He called. He's on his way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在露台上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The others are on the patio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我就当你是迎宾了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I take it you're the welcoming committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给我的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了你们今晚的表演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw your performance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我表达对你们的仰慕之情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May I extend my appreciation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲会很开心的，你是…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father will be delighted, Mr...? Mr...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆士·寇克，进取号舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain James Kirk, starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're honoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我原希望今晚能和令尊单独见面的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had hoped to meet your father here tonight personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，寇克上校，他不喜欢见客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, Captain Kirk, he has a rigid rule about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他从没和别人单独见过面，他也不参加派对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He never sees anyone personally, and he never attends parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,演员拒绝他的仰慕者啊？不常见啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An actor turning away his admirers? Very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里迪安是个很不寻常的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Karidian is a most unusual man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过“麦克白”了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You saw Macbeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我就跟“麦克白夫人”谈谈好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, then I’ll talk to Lady Macbeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号舰长，有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So captain of the Enterprise, interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克白夫人，也很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So Lady Macbeth, interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们下一步什么打算？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's your next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在贝妮莎演两场剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We play two performances at Benecia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,“女王星号”会带我们去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if the Astral queen can get us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是艘很好的星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's a good ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你演的麦克白夫人让人印象很深刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were very impressive as Lady Macbeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己本人呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And as Lenore Karidian?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,同样让人印象深刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾诺尔…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lenore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- …我想能再见到你 - 你是指演出吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...I'd like to see you again. - You mean professionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,未必\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想能和你再见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，我们有行程要赶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, we must keep a schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在没行程，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have a schedule now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我们离开这儿吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我才刚到 - 我也是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But I’ve only just arrived. - So have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不喜欢在欢迎会上逗留太久 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And you hate to overstay a welcome. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那好吧 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why not? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟女主人说一声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll make our apologies to our hostess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们门外见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll meet you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走累了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tired of walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，只是在想事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在派对上，你是那么强势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the party, you were such a brash young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在呢？ - 有点不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And now? - Now somehow different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是星舰的舰长，不是那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not a ship's captain, with all those people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有人面前强势自信的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be strong and confident in front of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很可爱，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you're really very dear, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在某种程度上…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In some ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,…非常孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是汤姆·雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Tom Leighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他现在安息了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least he has peace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,以前他从没安宁过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He never really had that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，要是汤姆的怀疑不属实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, why was Tom killed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他怎么会被杀？ - 我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- if what he suspected wasn't true? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽力找出真相的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll try and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Jim,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会多想念他啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how I’ll miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克呼叫进取号 - 舰桥收到，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk to Enterprise. - Bridge here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我接通轨道站女王星号的舰长琼·戴利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put me through to Captain Jon Daily of the Astral queen on orbit station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请尽快，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And put it on scramble, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,戴利舰长在线上，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Daily's on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,琼，我是吉姆·寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jon, Jim Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hi, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我个忙吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you do me a favour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠你多着呢，尽管说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I owe you a dozen, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要接你的乘客 - 你想让这些演员滞留在这吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't make your pickup here. - You mean strand all those actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我来接他们，出什么麻烦的话，责任我来背\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll pick them up. And if there's any trouble, it'll be my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，还有其他的事吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will do. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事请务必保密，请接受我的谢意，完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just keep this between the two of us and accept my thanks. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克呼叫进取号 - 舰桥收到，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk to Enterprise. - Bridge here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,传送室，准备传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Transporter Room, ready to beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,准备恢复原航线，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to resume course, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该接客人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think we're due for a pickup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的？人员还是货物？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What kind? Personnel? Cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，有位卡里迪安小姐被传到舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, a Miss Karidian has been transported aboard ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她要求见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She requests permission to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让她到舰桥上来 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell her to come up to the bridge. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,陪同卡里迪安小姐前往舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Escort Miss Karidian to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这位小姐要来？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you know this lady was coming aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长，没想到我们这么快就再见面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk, I didn't think we'd be meeting again so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我告诉你这是我安排的，你可能不会相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you probably wouldn't believe me if I told you I arranged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不会，你这样说让我很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, but it's a delightful thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，恐怕我们需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I'm afraid we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被滞留了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been stranded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似我们的交通工具拒绝我们搭乘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It seems that our transportation has cancelled out on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不能另外安排吗？ - 有，不过时间来不及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Can't you make other arrangements? - Well, yes, but not in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的计划就像一串链条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, our schedule is like a chain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一环出错，整串链条就会断裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One break, and it all collapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那样就太遗憾了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be a shame if that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有个好心人帮我们就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If ever we needed a Good Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I appeal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的章程对搭载乘客有明确规定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The regulations are very clear about taking on passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你做个交易，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll make a bargain with you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要拿什么做交易？ - 为全体舰员专场表演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What have you got to trade? - A special performance for the crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,换一次顺风船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in exchange for a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的提议很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You make it sound very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的舰员巡航好久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The crew has been on patrol for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以在单调中歇口气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They could use a break in the monotony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是答应了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我无法拒绝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got me backed into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他们看不到你们的演出，是不会放过我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The men would never forgive me if I deprived them of your performance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还有你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，舰长，我万分感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, captain. I'm eternally grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我让演出团准备一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll get the company ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这对他们太重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This means so much to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，卡里迪安的演出团一登舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, prepare to leave orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就准备驶离轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as soon as the Karidian Company is aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问问我们的目的地吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May I enquire as to our course, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,贝妮莎殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Benecia Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,贝妮莎殖民地离我们的目的地有八光年那么远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Benecia Colony is eight light years off our course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我脑子不灵光了，会马上告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If my memory needs refreshing, I'll ask you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前，执行我的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the meantime, follow my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2818.9\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2818.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are many questions in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很多的可能，来自演员卡里迪安和他的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}too many perhaps, about the actor Karidian and his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,个人来说，我几乎害怕知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For personal reasons, I am almost afraid to learn the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,预计到达时间，贝妮莎殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ETA, the Benecia colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在星历2825.3到达，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll arrive stardate 2825.3, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大概在当地时间15:00\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approximately 15:00 Benecia time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑图书馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Library computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,问题数据提交到人事档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Data on question submitted to personnel files.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,数据被接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Data being received.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,寇多斯档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kodos file.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所有幸存者中，有九名目击者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of all survivors, there are nine actual eyewitnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以认证寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who can identify Kodos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,停下，列出名单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop. Give list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克·J，现进取号舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk, J., presently Enterprise captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,雷顿·T，莫尔森·E\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leighton, T., Molson, E.,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利·K，伊姆斯·D\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley, K., Eames, D.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是星际服务部的上尉凯文·莱利吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that Star Service Lieutenant Kevin Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,确认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利·凯文，现任职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley, Kevin, presently assigned
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦星舰进取号通讯部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}USS Enterprise Communications section.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克 - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock. - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯部上尉凯文·莱利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Kevin Riley in Communications,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把他抽调到轮机甲板层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish to have him transferred down to the engineering decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是从轮机甲板层调任上来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He came up from Engineering, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把他送回去吧 - 有什么解释吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, I’m sending him back. - Any explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一名优秀的年轻官员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a fine young officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定认为这是纪律处分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's bound to consider this transfer a disciplinary action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想谈论这件事，史波克，请执行我的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't wish to discuss it, Mr. Spock. Please follow my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，高层领导往往踽踽独行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, the man on top walks a lonely street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,命令的链锁是个锁套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The chain of command is often a noose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我说你的哲学隐喻了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spare me your philosophical metaphors, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长的行为很古怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain is acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问你有没有注意到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm asking if you've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，你知不知道这周我头一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Negative. Do you know this is the first time in a week
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有时间喝喝酒？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I've had time for a drop of the true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来一杯，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you care for a drink, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父辈差点在酒精的诱惑下亡族灭种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father's race was spared the dubious benefits of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，现在我知道他们为什么被征服了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, now I know why they were conquered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛那么忧心忡忡？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you so worried about, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆做什么自己心里有数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I find Jim generally knows what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,载乘那些演员不合他的逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was illogical for him to bring those players aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不合逻辑？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Illogical?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那个小美人朱丽叶了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you get a look at that little Juliet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是一个让人怦然心动的尤物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a pretty exciting creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，你的个人特质让你屏蔽掉了这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, your personal chemistry would prevent you from seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有想过他也许仅仅是喜欢姑娘而已？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did it ever occur to you that he simply might like the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我排除了这一点 - 你当然会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I dismissed it. - You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他把上尉莱利调到轮机甲板层了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know that he transferred Lieutenant Riley to Engineering?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿发生的很多事我都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are lots of things that go on around here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I don't know, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他是舰长，他想怎么调就怎么调\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's the captain, he can transfer people as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把这看做是一百卷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can look that up in a hundred volumes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙规则的其中一种，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of space regulations somewhere, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦，来吧，喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. Now come on, have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不了，谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气，那我可喝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you're welcome, but I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，要是你不跟我一块喝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And please, Mr. Spock, if you won't join me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请别阻碍我喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}don't disapprove of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在你没尝过之前别这么做，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least not until you've tried it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是观测甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the observation deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是穿梭机所在的飞行甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's the flight deck down there with a shuttlecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有趣 - 对啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Interesting. - Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉我，寇克舰长 - 随便问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell me, Captain Kirk. - Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是为此专门点了柔光模式？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you order the soft lights especially for the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我点了柔光模式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I had ordered soft lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就顺便会安排音乐和鲜花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd also have arranged for music and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是，没这回事，在进取号上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, it isn't so. On the Enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽可能调成地球上白天黑夜的模式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we try to duplicate Earth conditions of night and day as closely as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,星光皎皎，明亮闪耀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Star light, star bright
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我心淼淼，太空逍遥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I may, I wish I might
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还记得吗，舰长？ - 流传很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you remember that, captain? - It's very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎和这些星球一样古老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost as old as the stars themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这艘星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的力量，穿梭航行，颠簸震动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All this power, surging and throbbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还是会平稳前行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}yet under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you like that, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这些力量全都在你的指挥之下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All this power at your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管你做出的这些决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yet the decisions that you have to make--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来自于一个地球人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come from a very human source.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是吗？地球人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you, captain? Human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这点不用怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说说你们星球上的女人，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me about the women in your world, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我更想知道关于你的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd rather talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定非常想表演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must have wanted to perform
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,从你第一次看到父亲的演出起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}since the first time you saw your father act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候？ - 最开始的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- When was that? - In the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来说说看 - 这不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell me about it. - That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没回答我关于女人的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't answered my question about the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道些什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What would you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是否已经被机器改造了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Has the machine changed them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,使得她们只是单纯的人类，而不是女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}made them just people instead of women?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,世界或许在变化，星系或许会解体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Worlds may change, galaxies disintegrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然而女人，一直是女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but a woman always remains a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,包括权利在内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and power too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所有星球的“凯撒”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Caesar of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,克里欧佩特拉（埃及艳后）也要崇拜他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Cleopatra to worship him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑图书馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Library computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要下列所有人的完整档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Full personal dossiers on the following names.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯·雷顿博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Thomas Leighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,安东·卡里迪安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anton Karidian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文·莱利上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Kevin Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和詹姆士·T·寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Captain James T. Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,已完成，待命中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Accomplished. Standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,核对他们的档案，查找关联项\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Correlate. Check their past histories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,报告所有在他们档案中共同出现的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report any item, any past episode or experience they all have in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,确认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你能为我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I appreciate whatever concern you may have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 星舰的和谐着想，史波克先生 - 我还是继续说吧，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- for the ship's company, Mr. Spock-- - I will continue, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我们电脑图书馆的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}According to our library banks,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,始于塔尔苏斯4号对地球的殖民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it started on the Earth colony of Tarsus IV
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那时大部分食物被一种外来的真菌污染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when the food supply was attacked by an exotic fungus and largely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,8000名殖民者实际上已经没有食物了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were over 8000 colonists and virtually no food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时，总督寇多斯获得独裁的权力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that was when Governor Kodos seized full power
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 并发布了紧急戒严令 - 我听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and declared emergency martial law. - I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许还不清楚事情的全部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may not have heard it all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,寇多斯开始将所有的殖民者划分成两部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kodos began to separate the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一部分人将获得定期的粮食补给得以存活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some would live, be rationed whatever food was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而剩下的那部分殖民者将面临死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The remainder would be immediately put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,显然，这是他自己的择优理论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, he had his own theories of eugenics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不幸地，他不是第一个这样做的人 - 或许不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Unfortunately, he wasn't the first. - Perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但这无疑是相当残忍的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But he was certainly among the most ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,随意决定谁生谁死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To decide arbitrarily who would survive and who would not,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就凭他个人的标准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}using his own personal standards,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,无情的执行这一决策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then to implement his decision without mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,父母就在孩子们的眼前死去，整个家庭就此瓦解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Children watching their parents die, whole families destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,4000多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Over 4000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一下子全死了，不再有任何痛苦，但他们已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They died quickly, without pain, but they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等救援到时已经晚了，已经无法挽回了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Relief arrived, but too late to prevent the executions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而寇多斯，活不见人，死不见尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Kodos, there never was a positive identification of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但这和卡里迪安有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what has Karidian to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里迪安的出现，几乎就从寇多斯失踪那天开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His history begins almost to the day where Kodos disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你认为吉姆怀疑他是寇多斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you think Jim suspects he's Kodos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,希望如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'd better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有九位目击者在那场大屠杀中幸存下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were nine eyewitnesses who survived the massacre,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都亲眼见过寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who had actually seen Kodos with their own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆·寇克就是其中一人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim Kirk was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,除了莱利和舰长寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With the exception of Riley and Captain Kirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的目击者都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}every other eyewitness is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后电脑图书馆的记录显示，无论他们在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And my library computer shows that wherever they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,地球，殖民地，还是飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on Earth, on a colony or aboard ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里迪安的演员们都离他们的死亡现场不远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Karidian Company of Players was somewhere near when they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，娱乐室的各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Rec Room, somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,回句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是拉里·马特森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Larry Matson here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗，莱利？什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that you, Riley? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不是我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个我已经死在轮机室了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am down in the Engineering Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就是说你表现的不乖了？ - 也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- So you've been a bad boy? - Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我做了什么，他们还是什么都不对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever I’ve done, they're sure keeping it a secret from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，是乌乎拉在弹琴吗，让我和她说几句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, is that Uhura playing? Let me talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他现在很受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think his heart is sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我能为你做些什么呢，莱利？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What can I do for you, Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弹一曲吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A song.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来首情歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make it a love song.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我感到慰藉就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just something to reassure me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我觉得自己不是这宇宙唯一的活物，恩？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not the only living thing left in the universe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对，你不是，我将证明给你看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you're not. I'll prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,阴沉又昏暗的天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The skies are green and glowing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.57,0:24:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,香味从哪飘来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where the scented
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.78,0:24:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮花在绽放着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lunar flower's growing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.00,0:24:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在远离星系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,远离心大星的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,某处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beyond Antares
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.09,0:24:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.64,0:25:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,即使渡过无限的岁月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Though it takes forever
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.35,0:25:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is just a day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,成了永远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是再次的旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is just another journey
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.66,0:25:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在路边小憩片刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A stop along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.13,0:25:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让岁月就这样流走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then let the years go fading
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.84,0:25:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.48,0:25:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爱在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where my love eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.15,0:25:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,永远的等着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.98,0:25:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在远离星系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.95,0:26:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,远离心大星的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.49,0:26:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,某处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beyond Antares
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得如何，莱利？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How'd you like that, Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.81,0:26:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快救救我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.08,0:26:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须得治好他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to pull him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.37,0:26:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不一定能行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not sure I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.21,0:26:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.75,0:26:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那么唯一能指证寇多斯的人就只有舰长了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the only one who'll be able to identify Kodos is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.67,0:26:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他将成为下一个目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he'll be the next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.01,0:27:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，星历2819.1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2819.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.18,0:27:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,船员莱利的状况正在恶化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's Officer Riley's condition worsening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生正在研究病因和研制解药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy making lab analysis to determine cause and antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.81,0:27:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都非常的担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Entire crew deeply concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.11,0:27:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,至今，实验数据显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As of this date, lab report indicates presence
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.36,0:27:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他摄入了大量的四氢化萘铋溶胶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of appreciable amount of tetralubisol,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.53,0:27:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,高挥发性的飞船专用的润滑剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a highly volatile lubricant in use aboard ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想毒死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone tried to poison him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.83,0:27:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,四氢化萘铋溶胶是种乳白色的物质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tetralubisol is a milky substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.75,0:27:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人容易混淆，误放了进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone could've gotten careless, made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.75,0:27:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都不相信这点，我想让船长过目这份报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe that, neither do you. I want the captain to see that report.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.25,0:27:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先等我完成记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I've finished logging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.75,0:27:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.13,0:27:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.43,0:27:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 关于上尉莱利的报告 - 他现在状况如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- My report on Lieutenant Riley. - Will he make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.48,0:27:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很大机会康复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's got a good chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.19,0:28:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们就此预测你的命运如何，船长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can we predict the same for you, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.78,0:28:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，史波克先生，我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, Mr. Spock, let's have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.74,0:28:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你和莱利上尉都是目击者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Riley was a witness. So were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.12,0:28:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 有人想杀害他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All right. - Someone tried to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.71,0:28:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也可能是场意外 - 你应该明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Could've been an accident. - You should be told the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.42,0:28:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是固执己见还是相信经验，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between empiricism and stubbornness, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.13,0:28:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一样，我也通过电脑图书馆核查过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I checked with the library computer just as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.93,0:28:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也得到了相同的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got the same information.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.47,0:28:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的是不是有点过分了，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aren't you getting a little out of line, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.56,0:28:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我的私事 - 这也与我有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- My personal business-- - Is my personal business
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当此事威胁到飞船的正常运作的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when it might interfere with the smooth operation of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.98,0:28:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得有这个可能？ - 有这可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You think that happened? - It could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.81,0:28:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢任何人插手我的私事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't like anyone meddling in my affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.61,0:28:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只要我是舰长就不能 - 吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- not even my second in command. - Jim,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.94,0:28:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克只是想… - 我知道他想干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock's simply trying-- - I know what he's trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.49,0:28:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的工作，你也清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's his job, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.24,0:28:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道，什么都还没有证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you also know that nothing is proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是在宇宙的这个角落里，船长，2加2还是等于4\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even in this corner of the galaxy, captain, two plus two equals four.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.96,0:28:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显，有人想试图杀害你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost certainly, an attempt will be made to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.50,0:28:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何要引火烧身？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you invite death?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.55,0:29:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只相信正义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm interested in justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.84,0:29:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.68,0:29:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定这不是一场复仇？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you sure it's not vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.43,0:29:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.73,0:29:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.40,0:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在做前所未有的尝试了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've done things I've never done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.19,0:29:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在以我的前途“赌博”了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've placed my command in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.28,0:29:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但从现在起，我必须要确定卡里迪安是否就是寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From here on, I’ve got to determine whether or not Karidian is Kodos.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.53,0:29:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.57,0:29:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像非常肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sound certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能和你一样确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.45,0:29:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在指控他之前，我必须要确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before I accuse a man of that, I've got to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.46,0:29:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,20年前，我见过他一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw him once, 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.84,0:29:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,人会变，记忆也会变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Men change. Memory changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.17,0:29:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在我看来，他是位演员，他可以改变相貌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I look at him now, he's an actor. He could've changed his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.05,0:29:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,逻辑推断是不够的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Logic is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.10,0:29:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须用自己的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got to feel my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.89,0:29:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,百分百的确定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}make absolutely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.81,0:29:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定了他就是寇多斯又怎样？然后怎么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if you decide he is Kodos? What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.73,0:30:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道想扮演上帝，带着他的头颅向众人宣告你的胜利？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you play God, carry his head through the corridors in triumph?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.32,0:30:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,逝去的生命已无法挽回了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That won't bring back the dead, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.57,0:30:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们会瞑目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they may rest easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.41,0:30:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,事情是这样的，船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Logic, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.83,0:30:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雷顿博士被杀害时卡里迪安的剧团刚好在Q星球上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Leighton was murdered while the Karidian Company was on Planet Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.21,0:30:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，又有人想试图杀害莱利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now an attempt has been made against Riley
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.09,0:30:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好他们剧团就在我们船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while the company is onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.51,0:30:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,医生还无法断定这就是一起谋杀案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doc isn't sure there was a murder attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.42,0:30:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,并且，我已经有办法证明…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Besides, I have an idea that may prove--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.80,0:30:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听，你听到没？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen. Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.89,0:30:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 低沉的嗡嗡声 - 是相位枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That low hum. - A phaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.35,0:30:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,超负荷状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.19,0:30:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.61,0:30:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有台超负荷的相位枪在我房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a phaser on overload in my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.48,0:30:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦爆炸，将炸穿整个甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it blows, it'll take out the entire deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.40,0:30:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所有在爆炸范围内的人员迅速撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Evacuate all personnel in this quadrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.90,0:30:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,2级红色警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Double red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.03,0:30:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你快出去 - 你也不能呆在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You get out of here. - You can't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.87,0:30:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快，封锁这片区域，快走，我来找\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go on, block off this section. Hurry, I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.71,0:30:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,迅速离开这片区域，马上封锁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Evacuate this section. Seal it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.42,0:31:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,清空C4和C5区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Clear sections C4 and C5.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.53,0:32:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早该谈谈了，不是么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're overdue for our talk, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.20,0:32:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能够尊重我的隐私，船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had hoped you would've respected my privacy, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.87,0:32:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就在刚才，我们差点就被卷入爆炸之中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A moment ago, we narrowly averted an explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.00,0:32:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那威力足以摧毁数个甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which would've destroyed several decks of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.58,0:32:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前，又有人试图毒害我们的船员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before that, someone tried to poison one of my crewmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.67,0:32:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我表示遗憾 - 你肯定会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm sorry to hear that. - I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.88,0:32:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是寇多斯吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you Kodos?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.26,0:32:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我在问你话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I asked you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.52,0:32:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你相信我是吗？ - 我信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you believe that I am? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.89,0:32:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意相信，那么我就是寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I am Kodos, if it pleases you to believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是位演员，我有很多身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm an actor. I play many parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.86,0:32:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在确实是位演员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're an actor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但20年前呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What were you 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.91,0:33:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻些，船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Younger, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.91,0:33:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的年轻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Much younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.62,0:33:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.59,0:33:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你是否还记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's see if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.68,0:33:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个对着墙上的对讲机朗读一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Read this into that communicator on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.43,0:33:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的声音将被记录下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will be recorded,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.26,0:33:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去和寇多斯的声音文件对比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and compared to a piece of Kodos' voice film we have in our files.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.18,0:33:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这项检测精度很高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The test is virtually infallible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.98,0:33:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它将告诉我们你到底是卡里迪安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will tell us whether you're Karidian
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.27,0:33:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还是刽子手寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or Kodos the Executioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,准备就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready for voice test.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.28,0:33:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,掩饰你的声音是毫无意义的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Disguising your voice will make no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.91,0:33:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,革命非常的成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"The revolution is successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.42,0:33:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但人们的存活得依赖于严厉的措施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but survival depends on drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.84,0:33:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你的存在将会对安定的社会构成威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your continued existence represents a threat to the well-being of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.30,0:33:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的存活将会是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your lives mean slow death
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.26,0:34:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这殖民地上更有存活价值的殖民者的慢性毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the more valued members of the colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.89,0:34:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，我别无选择，将你们判处死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Therefore, I have no alternative but to sentence you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.85,0:34:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的死亡将不可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your execution is so ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.02,0:34:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,寇多斯，塔尔苏斯4号的总督\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Signed Kodos, Governor of Tarsus IV."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.49,0:34:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得这些话，并已将它们记下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember the words. I wrote them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.32,0:34:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎很了解这段文字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said them like you knew them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.74,0:34:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你就没看几眼稿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You hardly glanced at the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.91,0:34:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有快速学习的能力 - 你确定？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I learn my parts very quickly. - Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.17,0:34:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定没有在一群被胁迫的人面前发表过此类演讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sure you didn't act this role out in front of a captive audience
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.00,0:34:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在一群曾被你无情的夺去生命的人面前？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whom you blasted out of existence without mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.17,0:34:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉仁慈一词从你嘴里说出非常的不合适，船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I find your use of the word "mercy" strangely inappropriate, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.43,0:34:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,站在这的你，是当今高科技社会标志性的体现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here you stand, a perfect symbol of our technical society.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.27,0:34:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,机械化，电子化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mechanized, electronicized,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.52,0:34:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是一个完整的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and not very human.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.65,0:34:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你早已失去了人性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've done away with humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.20,0:35:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,通过利用自己的资源去努力实现伟大的理想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The striving of man to achieve greatness through his own resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.08,0:35:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,人类早已开始使用工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've armed man with tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.20,0:35:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为了卓越的奋斗还在继续，而寇多斯…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The striving for greatness continues. But Kodos--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.45,0:35:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇多斯，无论他过去是谁 - 还是现在是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kodos, whoever he was-- - Or is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.87,0:35:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,或者现在是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.04,0:35:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,寇多斯决定了他人的生死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kodos made a decision of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.09,0:35:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一些人必须得死，而另一些人也许能够存活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some had to die that others might live.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.13,0:35:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有着至高的决策权，船长，你应该能明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a man of decision, captain. You ought to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.84,0:35:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我所知道的只有4000人被无辜的屠杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I understand is that 4000 people were needlessly butchered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.23,0:35:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为了拯救剩下的4000人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In order to save 4000 others.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.39,0:35:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果当时的救援能再晚些到达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if the supply ships hadn't come earlier than expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.02,0:35:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你所谓的寇多斯也许将名垂青史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this Kodos of yours might have gone down in history as a great hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.07,0:35:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,事实并非如此，历史已作出判决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But he didn't, and history has made its judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.91,0:35:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你确信我就是寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're so sure that I’m Kodos,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.45,0:35:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不赶快杀了我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why not kill me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.24,0:35:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让这血腥的复仇迎接最终的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let bloody vengeance take its final course,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.54,0:35:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再来看看这样做又有何意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and see what difference it makes to this universe of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.54,0:35:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,美丽的世界依然存在，并未改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those beautiful words, well acted, change nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.59,0:35:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.59,0:36:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们仅仅是工具，就像这艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're merely tools, like this ship of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.59,0:36:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,20年前根本没有安东·卡里迪安的任何记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are no previous records to Anton Karidian prior to 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.56,0:36:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,血肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blood thins,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.94,0:36:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,已模糊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}body fails,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人最终为着失去的记忆心怀感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and one is finally grateful for a failing memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.45,0:36:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我已不再珍视生命，包括我自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I no longer treasure life, not even my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.29,0:36:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我累了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.75,0:36:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,过去已成空白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the past is a blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.26,0:36:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道的都已经清楚了吗，寇克舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you get everything you wanted, Captain Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.97,0:36:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我清楚了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I had gotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.90,0:36:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道的一切…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...everything I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.61,0:36:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不会活着走出这个房间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you might not walk out of this room alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.28,0:37:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在最好休息下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You better rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.71,0:37:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在你光辉的外表下暴露出了残暴，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a stain of cruelty on your shining armour, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.42,0:37:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你原本可以放过我们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You could've spared him and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.85,0:37:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说过使用工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You talked of using tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.56,0:37:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在你眼里，我也是工具，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was a tool, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.48,0:37:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一个被利用去对付我父亲的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A tool to use against my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.02,0:37:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始，也许是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the beginning, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.61,0:37:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但晚些时候，我想让自己能做的更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But later, I wanted it to be more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.86,0:37:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,晚些，一切都是晚那么一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Later. Everything's always later.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.53,0:37:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,晚些，最晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Later, latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.70,0:37:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.70,0:37:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是太晚了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Too late, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.71,0:37:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像这飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are like your ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.00,0:38:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,能力强大，但不能算作个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}powerful and not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的心里没有仁慈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no mercy in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他是寇多斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he is Kodos,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.55,0:38:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,则我对他已经够仁慈了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then I’ve shown him more mercy than he deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.64,0:38:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if he isn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.89,0:38:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不会伤害你们，会让你们在贝妮莎下船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then we'll let you off at Benecia, and no harm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.24,0:38:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.45,0:38:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人，能决定伤害是否已造成？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who are you to say what harm was done?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.58,0:38:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我该是什么人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who do I have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.37,0:38:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,治疗记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Medical log.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.75,0:38:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利上尉已顺利康复并不再受管制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Riley sufficiently recovered to be discharged,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.59,0:38:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是舰长仅将他的活动范围限于医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but captain has ordered him restricted to Sickbay
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.05,0:38:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,防止他与自称是卡里迪安…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to prevent contact with passenger who calls himself Karidian
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.30,0:38:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但被怀疑是刽子手寇多斯的乘客接触\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and is suspected of being Kodos the Executioner
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.64,0:38:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而寇多斯杀害了上尉的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and of murdering the lieutenant's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.69,0:39:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2819.8\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2819.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.65,0:39:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌疑人已被监视\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suspect under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.32,0:39:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,关键区域已进入双重戒备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strategic areas under double guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.15,0:39:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里迪安的演出照常进行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Performance of the Karidian Players taking place as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.08,0:39:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚，卡里迪安居然将为大家带来话剧《哈姆雷特》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tonight, the Karidian Players present Hamlet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.83,0:39:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为大家演绎另一个星际中的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}another in a series of living plays presented in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.30,0:39:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,将以忠于传统古典戏剧的方式演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}dedicated to the tradition of classic theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.38,0:39:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,《哈姆雷特》是在残酷的社会中诞生的一部残酷话剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamlet is a violent play about violent times,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时代，生命不值一文，欲望代表一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when life was cheap and ambition was God.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.15,0:39:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信匹配的很完全了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe we have a match, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.11,0:39:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还不完全，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not an exact match, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.53,0:39:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是在决定一个人的生死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're dealing with a man's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.45,0:40:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不能把决定权交给机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No machine can make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.37,0:40:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在漫长的医学史中，没有哪位医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the long history of medicine, no doctor has ever caught
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.87,0:40:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能够及时地赶到现场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the first few minutes of a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.75,0:40:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利，别忘了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley, don't forget that--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.75,0:40:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.55,0:40:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克舰长，我是麦考依 - 收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain Kirk, McCoy here. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.09,0:40:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利不见了 当时我正在记录有关卡里迪安和寇多斯的事项\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley's gone. I was recording my log about Karidian and Kodos.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.89,0:40:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果被他听到了… - 我已经了解了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- If he overheard-- - You've made your point, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.26,0:40:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这里是H甲板的安全中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain. Security, H Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.10,0:40:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,武器库的锁已被破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The weapons locker has been broken into.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.27,0:40:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,遗失了一把相位枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One phaser is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.98,0:40:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是舰长，警备人员请注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the captain. Security two alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.11,0:40:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,找到并控制住上尉莱利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find and restrain Lieutenant Kevin Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.23,0:40:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他带着武器并很有可能前往剧院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's armed and possibly headed towards the ship's theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.92,0:41:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“你要把我带去哪里？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wither wilt thou lead me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.84,0:41:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,“说，我哪里也不去”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Speak; I'll go no further.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.60,0:41:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“听好了”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.56,0:41:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“我听着”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.56,0:41:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“我的死期即将到来”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My hour is almost come,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.44,0:41:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,“当我引燃那折磨我的烈火”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I to sulf'rous and tormenting fires
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.81,0:41:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“我已放弃我自己时”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}must render up myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.28,0:41:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“快说，我在听”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Speak. I am bound to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.45,0:41:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“你才会复仇”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So art thou to revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.62,0:41:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“你才会聆听”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when thou shalt hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.95,0:41:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“我的灵魂依然是你的父亲”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am thy father's spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.00,0:41:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,“只因某些原因而行走夜路，走向灭亡”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}doomed for a certain term to walk the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.63,0:41:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利，快回医务室去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley, get back to the Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.55,0:41:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀了我的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He murdered my father and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.89,0:41:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许认错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.18,0:41:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要因为认错人而毁了你一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't throw away your life on a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.06,0:41:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我没认错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.19,0:41:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“但正因我不能说出我那囚室的秘密”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that I am forbid to tell the secrets of my prison house...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.82,0:41:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我听得出他的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.32,0:42:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那张脸，我见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That face, I know it. I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.74,0:42:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀了我父母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He murdered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“才折磨着你的心智”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}--would harrow up thy soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.20,0:42:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,“冻结了你的鲜血”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}freeze thy young blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.16,0:42:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.29,0:42:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,把武器给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give me the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.59,0:42:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果你曾经爱过你的父亲”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If thou didst ever thy dear father love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.30,0:42:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就回医务室去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now get back to the Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.47,0:42:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.86,0:42:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美的演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's going beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.69,0:42:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，出了什么问题？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.19,0:42:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,脑海里总有个过去的声音纠缠着我，折磨着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was a voice out of the past haunting me, torturing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.78,0:42:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很早以前我曾经出演过另一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was another part I once played long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.37,0:42:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来都没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never told you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.79,0:42:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，同样的剧情再次上演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now that same curtain rises again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.87,0:42:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 时候到了 - 不，父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The time has come. - No, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.21,0:42:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那一刻永远也不会到来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The time will never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.71,0:43:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚，我演出结束过后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tonight, after my performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.55,0:43:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,最后两个能够伤害你的人将会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the last two who can harm you will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.34,0:43:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在说什么 - 本来有9个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What are you saying? - There were nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.14,0:43:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只剩两人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now there are only two,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.01,0:43:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们马上就会消失的，只要我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they will be gone as soon as I have--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.81,0:43:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.19,0:43:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了些什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.40,0:43:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What had to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.28,0:43:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必须得死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had to be silenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.24,0:43:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的那些人？那七个人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of them? All seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.16,0:43:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我双手又沾上了鲜血？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More blood on my hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.74,0:43:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不，父亲，不会再有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Father, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.08,0:43:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我很强大，父亲，没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm strong, Father. It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.17,0:43:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,第二幕，还有3分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Second act, three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.00,0:43:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.71,0:43:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.59,0:43:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的鬼魅都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the ghosts are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.34,0:43:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲手将他们葬送的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've buried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.59,0:43:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会再沾上鲜血的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no more blood on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.10,0:43:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子，我的孩子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My child, my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.27,0:43:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你已让我一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've left me nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.11,0:44:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是唯一一个没有受我当年恶行牵连的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were the one thing in my life untouched by what I’d done.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.28,0:44:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但你现在安全了，父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you're safe now, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.53,0:44:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经拯救了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.95,0:44:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，没人能伤害你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now no one can touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.33,0:44:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not even Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.55,0:44:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See Caesar come.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.39,0:44:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他敬畏你的伟大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is awed by your greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.15,0:44:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你耀眼的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your shining brightness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.49,0:44:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如刀刃般光亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bright as a blade
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在剑刃染上鲜血之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before it is stained with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.08,0:44:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如刀刃般光亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bright as a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.87,0:44:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩都过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come with me, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.21,0:44:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.92,0:45:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等表演结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}after the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.46,0:45:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,演出已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The play is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.00,0:45:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,20年前就该结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been over for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.80,0:45:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是名出征的战士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was a soldier in a cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.13,0:45:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要执行很多残酷的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were things to be done, terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.26,0:45:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下，父亲，你什么都不必说明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop it, Father. You have nothing to justify.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.18,0:45:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀，逃亡，自杀，癫疯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Murder, flight, suicide, madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.52,0:45:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来都不希望你从我的双手沾到鲜血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never wanted the blood on my hands ever to stain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.48,0:45:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么做是为了你，我已经救了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did it for you. I've saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.48,0:45:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,通过杀害那七个无辜的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By killing seven innocent men.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.44,0:45:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是无辜的，他们是个威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They weren't innocent. They were dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.28,0:45:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是毁灭整个世界我也要拯救他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would've killed a world to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.82,0:45:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,帷幕已升起，还有一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Curtain going up, one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.91,0:45:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，他必须要出演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The play, captain, he must go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.67,0:45:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他是伟大的卡里迪安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the great Karidian.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.38,0:45:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 警卫 - 你不能取消他…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Guard. - You cannot deny him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.38,0:45:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his last performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.72,0:45:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾诺尔，不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lenore, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.77,0:46:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是逃不出去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll never get off the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.73,0:46:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里将成为一个漂浮的坟场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will become a floating tomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.07,0:46:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在星际间飘荡…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}drifting through space...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.90,0:46:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,…伴随着伟大的卡里迪安的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...with the soul of the great Karidian
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.07,0:46:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有到过的星球上演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}giving performances at every star he touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.25,0:46:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道该如何使用，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know how to use this, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.04,0:46:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 - 暴君\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.59,0:46:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的死期到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}beware the Ides of March.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.17,0:46:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，孩子，不要！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, child, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.18,0:46:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.03,0:46:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,自豪的死去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}O proud Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.95,0:46:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在如此血腥的谋杀之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what feast is toward in thine eternal cell
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.29,0:47:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,尊贵的你，在你无尽的囚牢中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that thou such a prince
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.08,0:47:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,享用无尽的盛宴吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at a shot so bloodily has struck?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.30,0:47:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,帷幕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.64,0:47:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帷幕升起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The curtain rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.93,0:47:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它升起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.81,0:47:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间睡觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Tis no time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.86,0:47:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这剧本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The play.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.28,0:47:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,凭着这一本戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The play's the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.74,0:47:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们明白国王的良知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}wherein we'll catch the conscience of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.95,0:48:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,医疗记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Medical report.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.83,0:48:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她会受到最好的照顾，吉姆，她什么也不记得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She'll receive the best of care, Jim. She remembers nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.87,0:48:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她甚至还认为她父亲还活着，还在演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She even thinks her father's still alive, giving performances
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.50,0:48:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在欢呼的观众面前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before cheering crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.59,0:48:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的关心她，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You really cared for her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.05,0:48:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,准备脱离贝妮莎轨道，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to leave Benecia orbit, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.64,0:48:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,莱斯利先生，请待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by, Mr. Leslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.06,0:48:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所有频道可用吗，乌乎拉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All channels cleared, Uhura?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.27,0:48:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所有频道可用，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All channels clear, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.93,0:48:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等你就绪，莱斯利先生 - 正在脱离轨道，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Whenever you're ready, Mr. Leslie. - Leaving orbit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.77,0:48:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不打算回答我的问题，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not gonna answer my question, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.24,0:49:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,以一级曲速前进，莱斯利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ahead warp factor 1, Mr. Leslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.24,0:49:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.36,0:49:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.82,0:49:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏
